snippet.title: Soukoku no Kusabi: Hiiro no Kakera 3 - Ashita e no Tobira OP (Sotsugyou)
snippet.description:
Soukoku no Kusabi: Hiiro no Kakera 3 - Ashita e no Tobira OP for PSP
**I OWN NOTHING!!**
The game was just released last May 17. I think Fujita-san's new single is yet to be released. I don't know the title of this song yet. Does anyone know? Feel free to leave a comment! :D
